# Modern To-Do Application Plan

I will build a premium, highly aesthetic To-Do List application using vanilla HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The focus will be on a fluid user experience and modern UI design.

## User Review Required

- **Design Style**: I am planning a "Glassmorphism" aesthetic with vibrant gradients and smooth micro-animations.
- **Privacy**: Data will be stored locally in the browser (`localStorage`). No external backend is required.

